# If this is a new install
# 1) Run the script configure_partitions.sh, this will generate a new script install_partitions.sh
# 2) If you are happy with the script install_partitions.sh the run it
# 3) If successful you may reboot and remove the usb stick
#
# If this is an upgrade
# 1) Run the script install_bootloader.sh
# 2) If successful you may reboot and remove the usb stick
